title: https://github.com/eth-brownie
body:
### Environment information

* `brownie` Version: 1.17.2
* `ganache-cli` Version: Ganache CLI v6.12.2 (ganache-core: 2.13.2)
* `solc` Version: 1.1.1
* Python Version: 3.10.1
* OS: Windows 10 Education (OS Build 19042.1466)

### What was wrong?

>> brownie run .\scripts\deploy.py
